fields.description: AirPods Pro feature Active Noise Cancellation for immersive sound. Transparency mode for hearing the world around you. They’re sweat and water resistant1 and have a customizable fit for all-day comfort.

SoundLink Revolve Bluetooth® speaker Triple Black. Small speaker. Big leap forward. Deep. Loud. And immersive, too. To make something so small feel so real, Bose took its sound in a new direction. Every direction. But don’t let the size of the SoundLink® Revolve speaker fool you. It’s the kind of performance you might not expect from this pint-sized enclosure.
